details.text:
This section contains a summary of the area data generated by compiling the components through Quartus.
To generate the data, run a Quartus compile on the project created for this design. To run the Quartus compile:
1) Change to the quartus directory (./streamV1.prj/quartus)
2) quartus_sh --flow compile quartus_compile
